title: Map of British imports and exports in 19th century

content.question: The trade patterns shown on the map above depict

choices.label: British imports of raw materials and exports of finished goods during the nineteenth century
major slave trading routes in the nineteenth century
British trade routes that developed as a result of the disruption caused by the First World War
illicit drug routes that developed in the second half of the twentieth century

content.answer: British imports of raw materials and exports of finished goods during the nineteenth century
